ate="inactive" data-orientation="vertical" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2p8rr2:-trigger-ab3c9bd0-d77c-471d-9e6d-b7a9ae3288d51" id="radix-:R2p8rr2:-content-ab3c9bd0-d77c-471d-9e6d-b7a9ae3288d51" tabindex="0" style="display:none"><div data-rid="0ebd950f-331e-4b06-8bbf-0bd27fa4e21c" class="r-4e6i3u"><div data-rid="493ac7d2-daba-459a-853a-61bb5a26287d" class="r-14f1i27 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Simply&nbsp;add Hen Harmony to your flock’s drinking water based on the total amount of water in the waterer. Mix thoroughly before offering to hens.</p><p><br></p><h3>How Often Should I Use It?<br></h3><p><strong>1–8 chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every 3 months</strong><br><br></p><p><strong>9–14 chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every 2 months</strong><br></p><p><br><strong>15–21+ chickens</strong><br>• Use <strong>1 pouch every month</strong></p></span></div></div></div><div data-state="active" data-orientation="vertical" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2p8rr2:-trigger-8d9953c1-cc12-4ae0-9174-996454dd11e82" id="radix-:R2p8rr2:-content-8d9953c1-cc12-4ae0-9174-996454dd11e82" tabindex="0" style="display:contents;animation-duration:0s"><div data-rid="46432e67-ca14-40b5-b390-5e531c1b1c7c" class="r-3q9djw"><div data-rid="fbb8cb01-680a-43bd-959b-30f66686c310" class="r-cf2j1c alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>💧 <strong>Supports hydration & electrolyte balance during stress</strong><br>Heat, cold, and stress can quickly disrupt fluid balance. This helps support hydration and electrolytes so hens can maintain normal function during demanding conditions.</p><p><br></p><p>🦠 <strong>Supports gut balance & beneficial bacteria</strong><br>Stress can upset digestive balance. This helps support a healthy gut environment so digestion stays steady when hens are under pressure.<br><br>🐔<strong>Helps hens cope with heat, cold & environmental stress</strong><br>Seasonal and environmental changes can strain a hen’s system. This formula supports overall balance to help hens stay steadier through daily stressors.<br><br>🥚 <strong>Helps maintain steady egg production through seasonal stress </strong><br>Stress can affect normal laying patterns. By supporting hydration and digestion, this helps maintain nutritional support needed for normal egg production.<br><br>🇺🇸 <strong>Made in the USA with 100% natural, flock-safe ingredients</strong><br>Made in the USA with carefully selected, flock-safe ingredients—no harsh chemicals or unnecessary fillers.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="871c6814-409a-47ed-afb9-c5f1ee73f19b" class="r-4sx9di"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0046/3716/3633/files/wave-edge3.png?v=1740084237&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0046/3716/3633/files/wave-edge3.png?v=1740084237&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0046/3716/3633/files/wave-edge3.png?v=1740084237&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0046/3716/3633/files/wave-edge3.png?v=1740084237" alt="Green wave shape on a black background." class="r-q2ufod" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="02a3d6db-f546-495e-adb5-3f6db3f04400" class="r-1t0rp6s"><div data-rid="5f1bb347-5479-44f1-b4b4-b54ca4ca32b9" class="r-1c9g0c4"><div data-rid="aca400c0-67a6-4d84-b914-d452412aa4aa" class="r-nfgoa8" id="replo-carousel::R19rr2:" role="region" aria-label="Carousel" data-replo-carousel="true"><div aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true" class="replo-sr-only">Slide <!-- -->1<!-- --> of <!-- -->4</div><div data-rid="edba1cdd-fd08-48d8-a0ed-5bfacd183075" class="r-zd7a0"><div data-replo-component-root="carousel" data-replo-part="slides" data-replo-root-id="replo-carousel:Rv9rr2:" data-orientation="horizontal" data-active-slide-position="start" role="region" aria-l